Output assets/demo.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 12
Set Width 1100
Set Height 900
Set Theme "AtomOneLight"
Set Padding 16
Set TypingSpeed 55ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.25

Hide
  Type "cd /Users/adamthuvesen/dev/menti/biopsy"
  Enter
  Sleep 500ms
Show

Sleep 300ms
Type "uv run biopsy demo --rows 5000 --no-html"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 16s
